借nvme机器添加参数
ll /dev/disk/by-id 查看nvme的id
ibm-p8-garrison-03.rhts.eng.bos.redhat.com 
Kickstart Metadata: ignoredisk=--drives=disk/by-id/nvme-HUSPR3216AHP301_STM0001B6780

ibm-p8-garrison-04.rhts.eng.bos.redhat.com 
Kickstart Metadata: ignoredisk=--drives=disk/by-id/nvme-HUSPR3216AHP301_STM0001B67D7

在P8上加载vfio
modprobe vfio-pci disable_idle_d3=1
